title: The Forest House; Marion Zimmer Bradley .Mobi .Epub
description: The Forest House by Marion Zimmer Bradley.  I loved her as child and was heart broken when she died before finishing many of her works.  This is book two in the mists of Avalon series.  I hope you enjoy this book as much as I did I believe this happened before the Mists of Avalon and it explains the Mortal Coil. This contains the .epub and .mobi formats for easy reading on most devices. Enjoy and if you have other requests feel free to leave a comment.
